Translates Ultimate Fantastic Four #57 & Ultimate X-Men/Fantastic Four Annual #1.

America's longest-running magazine of classic comics now has twice as many pages of strips as the earlier version, on better paper, and includes 8 pages of full-color comic strips. This issue features "Monster of the Mountain," a complete Secret Agent Corrigan story by Al Williamson and Archie Goodwin. Plus, The Phantom, Flash Gordon, Mandrake the Magician, Tarzan, Little Orphan Annie, and many others.
